The project includes RESTful APIs built with Django REST Framework. API endpoints are available at `/api/`:

- **Listings API**: `/api/listings/`
- **Offers API**: `/api/offers/`
- **Messages API**: `/api/messages/`
- **Ratings API**: `/api/ratings/`

API documentation can be accessed via DRF's browsable API interface when running the development server.

